title: Alabama Senate Candidate Doug Jones Campaigns
description:
(28 Sep 2017) Alabama Democratic Senate candidate Doug Jones was in Birmingham Wednesday campaigning a day after Roy Moore won the GOP runoff.
At a restaurant he met with diners and media to discuss the differences in his candidacy and thoughts on fundraising.
He felt there could not be a clearer alternative to the Trump-lead GOP agenda. One supporter felt he was the answer to a perceived negative stereotype of Alabamians.
